CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 21, 1959, pg. A12, reads: "CELEBRATE WEDDING ANNIVERSARY - Mr. and Mrs. Reese Mosley, center, celebrated their 30th wedding anniversary with relatives and friends at their home... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Reese Mosley wearing striped tie, and Mrs. Mosley wearing corsage, standing behind cake on their 30th wedding anniversary, in home
